title: #115 - Texas Cattle Drive - Musician Grady Skelton, ME, & My Travelers - Dylan & Brad
description: Camping out in Texas while driving cattle, Musician Grady Skelton comes out for me, my travelers - Dylan & Brad, & my crew and plays some awesome original music and some amazing covers while I teach him a thing or two about improv'ing genius comedy songs...I am amazing - I am the Machine!!!
